@Leemoonsoo  the delivery orders do not matter. Since the call of broadcast on message 1 and the call of broadcast on message 2 would be processed one by one since `noteSocketMap` is synchronized. (in the latest code)

In this case, you are right. We may use other tricks to make the send operation concurrent.

I suggest we should use `parallelStream`.

